msgid "# DeepSeek-V4-Flash"
msgstr "# DeepSeek-V4-Flash"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 简介"

msgid "DeepSeek-V4 introduces several key upgrades over DeepSeek-V3:"
msgstr "DeepSeek-V4 在 DeepSeek-V3 的基础上引入了多项关键升级："

msgid ""
"- The Manifold-Constrained Hyper-Connections (mHC) to strengthen conventional residual connections.\n"
"- A hybrid attention architecture, which greatly improves long-context efficiency through Compress-4-Attention and Compress-128-Attention. For the Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) components, it still adopts the DeepSeekMoE architecture, with only minor adjustments."
msgstr ""
"- 流形约束超连接（mHC），用于增强传统的残差连接。\n"
"- 混合注意力架构，通过 Compress-4-Attention 和 Compress-128-Attention 大幅提升长上下文效率。对于混合专家（MoE）组件，仍采用 DeepSeekMoE 架构，仅做了少量调整。"

msgid ""
"DeepSeek-V4-Flash is the lightweight variant of the DeepSeek-V4 family, "
"suitable for high-throughput and low-latency serving scenarios."
msgstr "DeepSeek-V4-Flash 是 DeepSeek-V4 系列的轻量级变体，适用于高吞吐、低延迟的服务场景。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点与多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: Please replace the version placeholder above with your actual "
"validation version."
msgstr "> **注意**：请将上述版本占位符替换为您实际的验证版本。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

