msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid ""
"In this tutorial, we suppose you downloaded the model weight to "
"`/root/.cache/modelscope/hub/models/vllm-ascend/`. Feel free to change it to"
" your own path."
msgstr ""
"在本教程中，我们假设您已将模型权重下载到 `/root/.cache/modelscope/hub/models/vllm-"
"ascend/`。您可以根据需要将其更改为自己的路径。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended that the following service code be encapsulated in a .sh "
"script file and executed in Bash mode."
msgstr "建议将以下服务代码封装在 .sh 脚本文件中，并以 Bash 模式执行。"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node. The quantized model `DeepSeek-V4-Flash-w8a8-mtp` can be deployed on 1 "
"Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8) or 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8)."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode。量化模型 `DeepSeek-V4-Flash-w8a8-mtp` 可部署在 1 个 "
"Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）或 1 个 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"- `--max-model-len` specifies the maximum context length - that is, the sum of input and output tokens for a single request. Adjust it according to your actual scenario.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` indicates that prefix caching is disabled. To enable it, remove this option.\n"
"- `--speculative-config` configures the MTP (Multi-Token Prediction) speculative decoding to accelerate inference.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables full ACL graph execution in the decode phase to reduce scheduling latency.\n"
"- `--async-scheduling` enables asynchronous scheduling to overlap CPU scheduling with NPU computation.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` enables the FlashComm communication optimization."
msgstr ""
"- `--max-model-len` 指定最大上下文长度，即单个请求的输入和输出 token 之和。请根据实际场景调整。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` 表示禁用前缀缓存。如需启用，请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--speculative-config` 配置 MTP（多 token 预测）推测解码以加速推理。\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 在解码阶段启用全 ACL 图执行，以减少调度延迟。\n"
"- `--async-scheduling` 启用异步调度，使 CPU 调度与 NPU 计算重叠。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1` 启用 FlashComm 通信优化。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If you encounter issues, please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) for "
"troubleshooting."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如遇问题，请参考[公共 "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) 进行排查。"

msgid "Service Verification:"
msgstr "服务验证："

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-Node PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.2 多节点 PD 分离部署"

msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment: "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐使用 Mooncake "
"进行部署：[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid ""
"In the standard single-node deployment mode, Prefill (prompt processing) and"
" Decode (token generation) tasks run on the same set of NPUs. This can lead "
"to two issues:"
msgstr "在标准单节点部署模式下，Prefill（提示处理）和 Decode（token 生成）任务运行在同一组 NPU 上。这可能导致两个问题："

msgid ""
"1. **Prefill preemption interrupts Decode**: Prefill is a compute-intensive task that processes the entire input context at once, while Decode generates tokens one by one. When a new user request arrives, its Prefill phase can preempt and interrupt ongoing Decode tasks, causing jitter and higher time-per-output-token (TPOT) latency.\n"
"2. **Inflexible resource allocation**: Prefill and Decode have fundamentally different computational characteristics — Prefill is compute-bound and memory-bandwidth-intensive, while Decode is memory-bandwidth-bound. Running them on the same hardware forces a compromise that satisfies neither optimally."
msgstr ""
"1. **Prefill抢占中断Decode**：Prefill是计算密集型任务，一次性处理整个输入上下文，而Decode逐token生成。当新用户请求到达时，其Prefill阶段会抢占并中断正在进行的Decode任务，导致抖动和更高的单token输出延迟（TPOT）。\n"
"2. **资源分配不灵活**：Prefill和Decode具有根本不同的计算特性——Prefill受计算限制且内存带宽密集，而Decode受内存带宽限制。在同一硬件上运行两者会迫使做出折中，无法最优地满足任何一方。"

msgid ""
"PD (Prefill-Decode) separation addresses these issues by running Prefill and"
" Decode on dedicated node groups, each configured independently. This "
"architecture is recommended for production deployments with concurrent "
"multi-user workloads, where stable latency and high throughput are both "
"required."
msgstr ""
"PD（Prefill-"
"Decode）分离通过在专用节点组上独立运行Prefill和Decode来解决这些问题，每个节点组可独立配置。对于需要同时保证稳定延迟和高吞吐量的并发多用户生产环境，推荐采用此架构。"

msgid ""
"The following sections describe PD separation deployment on both Atlas 800 "
"A3 (128G × 8) and Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) multi-node environments."
msgstr "以下章节描述了在Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）和Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）多节点环境下的PD分离部署。"

msgid "#### 5.2.1 A3 Series PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "#### 5.2.1 A3系列PD分离部署"

msgid ""
"This section shows the deployment guide of DeepSeek-V4-Flash on Atlas 800 A3"
" (128G × 8) multi-node environment with 1P1D for better performance."
msgstr ""
"本节展示在Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）多节点环境下，采用1P1D配置部署DeepSeek-V4-Flash以获得更优性能的指南。"

msgid "Parameter descriptions:"
msgstr "参数说明："

msgid ""
"Refer to [Prefill-Decode Disaggregation "
"(Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) to deploy "
"the P-D disaggregation proxy."
msgstr ""
"请参考 [Prefill-"
"Decode分离（Deepseek）](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) "
"部署P-D分离代理。"

msgid "#### 5.2.2 A2 Series PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "#### 5.2.2 A2系列PD分离部署"

msgid ""
"This section shows the deployment guide of DeepSeek-V4-Flash on Atlas 800 A2"
" (64G × 8) multi-node environment with 4\\*1P 1\\*4D for better performance."
msgstr ""
"本节展示在Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）多节点环境下，采用4\\*1P "
"1\\*4D配置部署DeepSeek-V4-Flash以获得更优性能的指南。"

msgid "Before you start, please:"
msgstr "开始前，请："

msgid "1. Prefill node (4 P nodes share the same script)"
msgstr "1. Prefill节点（4个P节点共享同一脚本）"

msgid ""
"For each P instance, only these two configuration values need to be "
"modified: `kv_port` and `engine_id`. The `engine_id` should start from 0 and"
" increment sequentially, while the `kv_port` (e.g., `30100`) must be unique "
"for each P instance, such as 30000, 30100, etc."
msgstr ""
"对于每个P实例，只需修改以下两个配置值：`kv_port` 和 `engine_id`。`engine_id` 应从0开始依次递增，而 "
"`kv_port`（例如 `30100`）对于每个P实例必须唯一，如30000、30100等。"

msgid "2. Decode node (4 D nodes share the same script)"
msgstr "2. Decode节点（4个D节点共享同一脚本）"

msgid "1. Prefill node"
msgstr "1. Prefill节点"

msgid ""
"For each P instance, only the `--dp-address` parameter differs and must be "
"configured as the IP address of the service within the same subnet as the "
"other instances."
msgstr "对于每个P实例，只有 `--dp-address` 参数不同，必须配置为与其他实例在同一子网内的服务IP地址。"

msgid "2. Decode node"
msgstr "2. Decode节点"

msgid ""
"For each D instance, only the `--dp-rank-start` parameter differs, which "
"should be configured as 0, 8, 16, and 24 respectively. Each instance's "
"`--dp-address` must be set to the IP address of the main D node, which is "
"the IP of the Decode instance with `--dp-rank-start` set to 0."
msgstr ""
"对于每个D实例，只有 `--dp-rank-start` 参数不同，应分别配置为0、8、16和24。每个实例的 `--dp-address` "
"必须设置为主D节点的IP地址，即 `--dp-rank-start` 设置为0的Decode实例的IP。"

msgid "4. Deploy the P-D disaggregation proxy."
msgstr "4. 部署P-D分离代理。"

msgid ""
"The proxy is also implemented by referring to [Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
" (Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)."
msgstr ""
"该代理同样参考 [Prefill-"
"Decode分离（Deepseek）](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) "
"实现。"

msgid ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`: enables the communication optimization function on the prefill nodes.\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable: true`: enables the recomputation scheduler. When the KV Cache of the decode node is insufficient, requests will be sent to the prefill node to recompute the KV Cache. In the PD separation scenario, enable this configuration only on decode nodes.\n"
"- `MooncakeHybridConnector`: the KV transfer connector used for PD separation, transferring KV Cache between prefill and decode nodes.\n"
"- `enable_shared_expert_dp: true`: enables data parallelism for shared experts, applicable to MoE models."
msgstr ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1=1`：在prefill节点上启用通信优化功能。\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable: true`：启用重计算调度器。当decode节点的KV Cache不足时，请求将被发送到prefill节点重新计算KV Cache。在PD分离场景下，仅在decode节点上启用此配置。\n"
"- `MooncakeHybridConnector`：用于PD分离的KV传输连接器，在prefill和decode节点之间传输KV Cache。\n"
"- `enable_shared_expert_dp: true`：为共享专家启用数据并行，适用于MoE模型。"

msgid "Deployment Verification:"
msgstr "部署验证："

msgid ""
"After the PD separation service is fully started, send a request through the"
" proxy port on the prefill master node to verify that Prefill and Decode "
"nodes are working correctly together. Refer to [Prefill-Decode "
"Disaggregation "
"(Deepseek)](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) for the "
"proxy verification method."
msgstr ""
"PD分离服务完全启动后，通过prefill主节点上的代理端口发送请求，验证Prefill和Decode节点是否协同正常工作。代理验证方法请参考 "
"[Prefill-"
"Decode分离（Deepseek）](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If you encounter issues with PD separation deployment, "
"please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) for "
"troubleshooting."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果在PD分离部署中遇到问题，请参考 "
"[公共FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) 进行故障排除。"

msgid "#### 5.2.3 Ultra-Long Sequence Deployment"
msgstr "#### 5.2.3 超长序列部署"

msgid ""
"For ultra-long sequence scenarios, support can be achieved by adjusting the "
"PD (Prefill/Decode) ratio and the model parallelism strategy. For example, "
"in a 1M sequence scenario, a 1\\*4P-1\\*4D ratio can be used, with the model"
" parallelism set to DP4TP8 mode."
msgstr ""
"对于超长序列场景，可以通过调整PD（预填充/解码）比例和模型并行策略来提供支持。例如，在1M序列场景中，可以使用1\\*4P-1\\*4D的比例，并将模型并行设置为DP4TP8模式。"

msgid "## 6 Functional Verification"
msgstr "## 6 功能验证"

