msgstr "    |`--dp-size`|int|是|-|数据并行大小（所有节点上的DP rank总数）。|"

msgid "    |`--tp-size`|int|No|1|Tensor parallel size within each DP rank.|"
msgstr "    |`--tp-size`|int|否|1|每个DP rank内的张量并行大小。|"

