"    |`--dp-size-local`|int|No|(same as `--dp-size`)|Number of DP ranks on "
"the current node. If not set, defaults to `--dp-size`.|"
msgstr ""
"    |`--dp-size-local`|int|否|(与`--dp-size`相同)|当前节点上的DP "
