msgstr "    |`--dp-rank-start`|int|否|0|此节点上数据并行rank的起始偏移量。|"

msgid ""
"    |`--dp-address`|str|Yes|-|IP address of the data parallel master node.|"
msgstr "    |`--dp-address`|str|是|-|数据并行主节点的IP地址。|"

msgid ""
"    |`--dp-rpc-port`|str|No|12345|RPC port for data parallel master "
